      </div>
      <div class="team__grid">
        <article class="member" data-reveal>
          <div class="member__monogram">AG</div>
          <h3>Aimee Greenfield</h3>
          <p class="member__role">Owner · Broker-in-Charge, NC &amp; VA</p>
          <p class="member__bio">Certified Luxury Home Specialist with a background in interior design &amp; architecture.</p>
          <div class="member__contact">
            <a href={`tel:${site.phoneAimeeHref}`}>{site.phoneAimee}</a>
            <a href={site.whatsapp} target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="member" data-reveal>
          <div class="member__monogram">DC</div>
          <h3>David Collings</h3>
          <p class="member__role">NC Real Estate Broker · Premier Zillow Agent</p>
          <p class="member__bio">Nearly a decade in NC real estate; former GE Healthcare design engineering leader.</p>
          <div class="member__contact">
            <a href="tel:+13307148358">330-714-8358</a>
            <a href="mailto:dpccollings@gmail.com">Email</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="member" data-reveal>
          <div class="member__monogram">MC</div>
          <h3>Marilyn Collings</h3>
          <p class="member__role">Office Manager</p>
          <p class="member__bio">30+ years in HR and client service — the steady hand that keeps every closing on track.</p>
